                "title": "玉颗珊珊月中落"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，治疗我方受伤最多的角色1点。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_531857261936032450.png",
                "id": "talent99572",
                "key": "月桂 · 抛掷型",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/0f3a979856a1d439f1f85900b98bf648_5333621303159692565.png",
                "title": "月桂 · 抛掷型"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_4759235431490427600.png",
                "id": "talent85378",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">桂子仙机</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方切换角色后：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，治疗我方出战角色1点。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6499990925390015521.png",
